Description: The [Achievement Standards Network](http://asn.jesandco.org "Achievement Standards Network") (ASN) provides open access to machine-readable representations of learning objectives published by education agencies and organizations. This is the ASN:US dataset of "published" learning objectives.  The ASN is also used in Australia [(ASN:AU)](http://www.australiancurriculum.edu.au/Technical/Introduction "ASN:AU").The ASN is is funded in part by the [Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation](http://gatesfoundation.org "Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation") and was initially funded by the [National Science Foundation](http://www.nsf.gov/ "National Science Foundation").
